  "html": "<div class=\"hostis\"><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Alternative_forms\">Alternative forms</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=hostis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Alternative forms\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3><ul><li><span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=ostis&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"ostis (page does not exist)\">ostis</a></span> (<i><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medieval_Latin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Medieval Latin\">Medieval</a></i>)</li>\n<li><span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=fostis&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"fostis (page does not exist)\">fostis</a></span> (<i>rare</i>)</li>\n<li><span class=\"Latn\" lang=\"la\"><a href=\"/wiki/ost#Latin\" title=\"ost\">ost</a></span> (<i><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Medieval_Latin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Medieval Latin\">Medieval</a>, rare</i>)</li></ul><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Etymology\">Etymology</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=hostis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: Etymology\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3><p>From <span class=\"etyl\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Proto-Italic_language\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Proto-Italic language\">Proto-Italic</a></span> <i class=\"Latinx mention\" lang=\"itc-pro\"><a href=\"/wiki/Reconstruction:Proto-Italic/hostis\" title=\"Reconstruction:Proto-Italic/hostis\">*hostis</a></i>, from <span class=\"etyl\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Proto-Indo-European_language\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Proto-Indo-European language\">Proto-Indo-European</a></span> <i class=\"Latinx mention\" lang=\"ine-pro\"><a href=\"/wiki/Reconstruction:Proto-Indo-European/g%CA%B0%C3%B3stis\" title=\"Reconstruction:Proto-Indo-European/g&#x2B0;&#xF3;stis\">*g&#x2B0;&#xF3;stis</a></i> <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">&#x201C;</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\">guest, stranger</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">&#x201D;</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">)</span>, whence also <span class=\"etyl\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Proto-Germanic_language\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Proto-Germanic language\">Proto-Germanic</a></span> <i class=\"Latinx mention\" lang=\"gem-pro\"><a href=\"/wiki/Reconstruction:Proto-Germanic/gastiz\" title=\"Reconstruction:Proto-Germanic/gastiz\">*gastiz</a></i> and <span class=\"etyl\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Proto-Slavic\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Proto-Slavic\">Proto-Slavic</a></span> <i class=\"Latinx mention\" lang=\"sla-pro\"><a href=\"/wiki/Reconstruction:Proto-Slavic/gost%D1%8C\" title=\"Reconstruction:Proto-Slavic/gost&#x44C;\">*gost&#x44C;</a></i>.\n</p><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Pronunciation\">Pronunciation</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=hostis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: Pronunciation\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3><p><span class=\"ib-brac qualifier-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content qualifier-content\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Classical_Latin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Classical Latin\">Classical</a></span><span class=\"ib-brac qualifier-brac\">)</span> <a href=\"/wiki/Wiktionary:International_Phonetic_Alphabet\" title=\"Wiktionary:International Phonetic Alphabet\">IPA</a><sup>(<a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Latin_pronunciation\" title=\"Appendix:Latin pronunciation\">key</a>)</sup>: <span class=\"IPA\">/&#x2C8;hos.tis/</span>, <span class=\"IPA\">[&#x2C8;h&#x254;s.t&#x32A;&#x26A;s]</span>\n</p><ul><li><span class=\"ib-brac qualifier-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content qualifier-content\"><a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ecclesiastical_Latin\" class=\"extiw\" title=\"w:Ecclesiastical Latin\">Ecclesiastical</a></span><span class=\"ib-brac qualifier-brac\">)</span> <a href=\"/wiki/Wiktionary:International_Phonetic_Alphabet\" title=\"Wiktionary:International Phonetic Alphabet\">IPA</a><sup>(<a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Latin_pronunciation\" title=\"Appendix:Latin pronunciation\">key</a>)</sup>: <span class=\"IPA\">/&#x2C8;os.tis/</span>, <span class=\"IPA\">[&#x2C8;&#x254;s.t&#x32A;is]</span></li></ul><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Noun\">Noun</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=hostis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: Noun\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3><p><strong class=\"Latn headword\" lang=\"la\">hostis</strong>&#xA0;<span class=\"gender\"><abbr title=\"masculine gender\">m</abbr></span> (<i>genitive</i> <b class=\"Latn\" lang=\"la\"><strong class=\"selflink\">hostis</strong></b>); <i><a href=\"/wiki/Appendix:Latin_third_declension\" title=\"Appendix:Latin third declension\">third declension</a></i>\n</p><ol><li>an <a href=\"/wiki/enemy\" title=\"enemy\">enemy</a> of the <a href=\"/wiki/state\" title=\"state\">state</a>, a <a href=\"/wiki/stranger\" title=\"stranger\">stranger</a></li>\n<li><span class=\"ib-brac\">(</span><span class=\"ib-content\">plural only</span><span class=\"ib-brac\">)</span> the <a href=\"/wiki/enemy\" title=\"enemy\">enemy</a></li></ol><h4><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Declension\">Declension</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=hostis&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: Declension\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h4><p><a href=\"/wiki/Ap